title: Judging by the Cover
description: Regine is dating a new catch while Sinclair has forgotten to secure the front cover celebrity for Flava Magazine. Upon learning Regine's new man is a married man, Sinclair, Khadijah and Max must find a way to tell Regine without her getting upset.

title: Crappy Birthday
description: The girls strong-arm Khadijah into going to Atlantic City for her birthday leaving Overton and Kyle to 'water the plants' while they're gone.

title: Love Takes a Holiday
description: Khadijah and Synclaire ask their recently jolted co-worker to join them for a girls night out. Kyle falls for her but the feeling isn't entirely mutual.

title: Burglar in the House
description: Regine gets mugged and the girls fears that the mugger will break into their place comes true. Overton installs a security system and the fear of another break in sets in.

title: The Hand That Robs the Cradle
U.N.I.T.Y.
description: Kyle has to choose between a promotion and his friend when he hears his boss lie about his date with Regine.

title: Love Is a Many Splintered Thing
description: The girls feel neglected when Khadijah starts a new relationship.

title: A Tale of Two Tattles
description: Regine's new comedian boyfriend uses the girls' secrets in his act.

title: She Ain't Heavy, She My Mother
What's Next?
description: Khadijah has to choose between her new boyfriend and an old love.

title: There's Got to Be a Morning After
I Love This Game
description: Khadijah is challenged to a rematch by her school basketball rival when she accuses Khadijah of cheating to get an MVP trophy.

title: Am I My Sister's Keeper?
description: Overton's sister comes to visit. Kyle starts dating her and Overton disapproves.

title: Trick or Trust
description: The gang unsuccessfully try to scare Maxine during Halloween.

title: Abstinence Makes the Heart Grow Fonder
My Cups Runneth Over
description: Regine has to get a breast reduction.

title: There's No Ship Like Kinship
description: When Khadijah's friend, Sheri, starts working at "Flavor," Khadijah gets jealous of the closeness between Synclaire and Sheri.

title: He Works Hard for the Money
The Following Is a Sponsored Program
description: A discouraged Synclaire is unsure about auditioning for an infomercial for a dashboard grill, but Max encourages her to follow her acting aspirations. Regine volunteers Max to drive Synclaire to the audition in order to keep her from hanging around the apartment on her day off. Max confronts the director when he dismisses Synclaire without allowing her to say her lines. Meanwhile..Overton is racked with guilt when he continually dreams about the R&B group TLC after falling asleep during its videos.

title: Let It Snow, Let It Snow, Let It Snow... Dammit
Tibby or Not Tibby
description: This is the episode where Overton's favorite uncle, Tibby, tells Overton to dump Sinclair because she is too upbeat all the time. Meanwhile, Khadijah is trying to help Russell avoid deportation, and Max urges Kyle to date another woman.
